``` {.python .cell-code}
import pandas as pd
from pathlib import Path

p = Path('data/raw/verdicts.csv')
df = pd.read_csv(p)
df['judgment_date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['judgment_date'], errors='coerce')
df['year'] = df['judgment_date'].dt.year
counts = df.groupby('year').size().rename('n').reset_index()
counts
```
